{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775817926178,"sessionID":"ses_289035be8ffe3kGMnvWTGUwjuS","part":{"id":"prt_d76fcb924001YdKxGHJdB3Lr3o","messageID":"msg_d76fcafca001DuGU6YdFDonEwG","sessionID":"ses_289035be8ffe3kGMnvWTGUwjuS","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_f1febfba5b6a41138d669885","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore workloadmanager codebase","prompt":"I need to understand the agentcube project's `pkg/workloadmanager` module to write a proposal for \"AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\" (Sandbox deletion and lifecycle management). \n\nPlease thoroughly explore:\n\n1. The directory structure under `pkg/workloadmanager` - find all files\n2. Read the key files in `pkg/workloadmanager` to understand:\n   - How sandboxes/workloads are currently created\n   - Any existing deletion logic\n   - Lifecycle management patterns\n   - Interfaces and types used\n3. Look for any existing proposal.md files or design docs in the repo for format reference\n4. Check for any related specs or documentation about sandbox lifecycle\n5. Look at the project root for any ARCHITECTURE.md, README.md, or similar docs that give context\n\nReturn:\n- Full file listing of pkg/workloadmanager\n- Key type/interface definitions found\n- Current creation and deletion flow summary\n- Any existing lifecycle management code\n- Proposal format examples if found\n- Any relevant constants, configs, or enums related to sandbox states","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_289032c14ffevtNxPD1p7L2Iph (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the complete analysis:\n\n---\n\n## 1. Full File Listing of `pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  handler/\n    sandbox_create.go      (687 lines) -- Sandbox creation handlers\n    models.go              (57 lines)  -- Request/response models and types\n    constants.go           (53 lines)  -- GVRs, kind constants, labels, annotations, defaults\n  response/\n    response.go            (45 lines)  -- JSON response helpers\n    response_test.go       (108 lines) -- Response helper tests\n```\n\n**Total: 5 Go files** across 2 subpackages (`handler/`, `response/`).\n\n---\n\n## 2. Key Type and Interface Definitions\n\n### From `handler/models.go`:\n\n```go\ntype CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n    Kind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n    Name      string `json:\"name\"`\n    Namespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n}\n\ntype CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n    SessionID   string       `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxID   string       `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxName string       `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    EntryPoints []EntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n}\n\ntype EntryPoint struct {\n    Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n    Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n    Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    SessionID    string       `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxName  string       `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    SandboxID    string       `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    WorkloadName string       `json:\"workloadName\"`\n    Namespace    string       `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Kind         string       `json:\"kind\"`\n    PodIP        string       `json:\"podIp,omitempty\"`\n    EntryPoints  []EntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints,omitempty\"`\n    CreatedAt    time.Time    `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt    time.Time    `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status       string       `json:\"status\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxStatus struct {\n    Status string\n    Error  error\n}\n```\n\n### From `handler/sandbox_create.go` -- Interfaces used by the handler:\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, info *SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *SandboxInfo) error\n}\n\ntype SandboxReconcilerWatcher interface {\n    WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name string) (<-chan SandboxStatus, error)\n}\n\ntype TokenCache interface {\n    GetOrCreateUserK8sClient(namespace, saName, token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n}\n\ntype UserClientFactory interface {\n    CreateUserClient(token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n}\n```\n\n### From `handler/constants.go` -- GVRs, Kind constants, Labels, Annotations, Defaults:\n\n```go\n// GVRs\nAgentRuntimeGVR    = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes\nCodeInterpreterGVR = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/codeinterpreters\nSandboxGVR         = agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes\nSandboxClaimGVR    = extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims\n\n// Kind constants\nAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\nCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\nSandboxesKind       = \"Sandbox\"\nSandboxClaimsKind   = \"SandboxClaim\"\n\n// Labels\nLabelManagedBy      = \"app.kubernetes.io/managed-by\"\nLabelManagedByValue = \"agentcube-workload-manager\"\nLabelSessionID      = \"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"\nLabelWorkloadName   = \"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"\nLabelSandboxName    = \"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"\n\n// Annotations\nAnnotationIdleTimeout    = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\nAnnotationSandboxPodName = \"agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name\"\n\n// Defaults\nIdentitySecretName        = \"picod-router-identity\"\nPublicKeyDataKey          = \"public.pem\"\nDefaultSandboxTTL         = 8   // hours\nDefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15  // minutes\n```\n\n### Full Store Interface (from `session-store/design.md`):\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n    Close() error\n}\n```\n\n### SandboxInfo from `pkg/common/types` (the canonical version used by Store):\n\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n    SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n    Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n    EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n    SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. Current Creation Flow Summary\n\nThe sandbox creation flow (in `sandbox_create.go`) follows this pattern for both `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter`:\n\n1. **Parse & Validate Request** -- Bind JSON to `CreateSandboxRequest`, validate required fields\n2. **Lookup Template** -- Use informer lister to fetch the `AgentRuntime` or `CodeInterpreter` CR by name/namespace\n3. **Generate IDs** -- `SessionID` (UUID), `SandboxName` (`{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`)\n4. **Build Sandbox CR** -- Construct `unstructured.Unstructured` with:\n   - APIVersion: `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind: `Sandbox` (or `SandboxClaim` for warm pools)\n   - Labels: `managed-by`, `session-id`, `workload-name`, `sandbox-name`\n   - Annotations: `idle-timeout` from template's `SessionTimeout` or default 15m\n   - Spec: `replicas: 1`, `lifecycle.shutdownTime` = now + TTL (from `MaxSessionDuration` or default 8h), ports, podTemplate\n5. **StoreSandbox** -- Write placeholder `SandboxInfo` (status: \"pending\") to Redis/Valkey store\n6. **Register Watcher** -- `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, sandboxName)` for one-shot status notification\n7. **Create CR** -- `dynClient.Resource(gvr).Namespace(ns).Create(...)`\n8. **Wait for Running** -- Select on watcher channel with 2-minute timeout\n9. **Resolve Pod IP** -- Try sandbox name -> annotation -> label selector\n10. **UpdateSandbox** -- Update store with full info (status: \"running\", PodIP, EntryPoints, SandboxID)\n11. **Return Response** -- `CreateSandboxResponse` with SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n\n**Rollback**: If any step after CR creation fails, `rollbackCR()` deletes the created CR with a 30-second timeout context.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Existing Deletion Logic\n\n### Current deletion is limited to two mechanisms:\n\n#### A. Rollback during creation (`rollbackCR` in `sandbox_create.go`, lines 363-372):\n```go\nfunc (h *SandboxCreateHandler) rollbackCR(ctx context.Context, gvr schema.GroupVersionResource, namespace, name string, dynClient dynamic.Interface) error {\n    rollbackCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, 30*time.Second)\n    defer cancel()\n    err := dynClient.Resource(gvr).Namespace(namespace).Delete(rollbackCtx, name, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n    if err != nil && apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n        return nil\n    }\n    return err\n}\n```\n\n#### B. Garbage Collector (described in `sandbox-orchestration/design.md`):\n- Background goroutine ticks every **15 seconds**\n- Per tick: `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, now - DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout, 16)` and `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, now, 16)` -- batch size 16\n- Single tick context timeout: **2 minutes**\n- Merges both lists, deletes each unique workload, then removes store entry by session ID\n\n#### C. Delete endpoint (planned but NOT yet implemented):\nThe spec (`sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`) defines the requirement:\n- `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` and `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId`\n- Load session from store by `sessionId`; on `ErrNotFound` return 404\n- Delete `SandboxClaim` when stored `Kind` is `SandboxClaim`, else delete `Sandbox`\n- Treat API `NotFound` on delete as success\n- Then `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` from store\n- Success response: `200 {\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n\n#### D. Idle Cleanup Controller (`agentd`):\n- Separate controller in `pkg/agentd` that watches `Sandbox` CRs\n- Reads annotation `last-activity-time`\n- If `time.Now().After(lastActivity + 15m)`, deletes the Sandbox\n- Requeues with `time.Until(expirationTime)` if not yet expired\n\n---\n\n## 5. Lifecycle Management Patterns\n\n### Sandbox States (implicit, not an enum):\n- `\"pending\"` -- Initial state when `StoreSandbox` is called\n- `\"running\"` -- After Pod IP resolved and `UpdateSandbox` called\n\n### Lifecycle properties set on Sandbox CR:\n- **TTL (Time-To-Live)**: `lifecycle.shutdownTime` = `now + MaxSessionDuration` (default 8h)\n- **Idle Timeout**: annotation `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` = `SessionTimeout` (default 15m)\n- **Last Activity**: annotation `last-activity-time` (read by agentd for idle cleanup)\n\n### Lifecycle management is distributed across multiple components:\n1. **WorkloadManager** -- Creates sandboxes, has rollback on creation failure\n2. **SandboxReconciler** -- Watches for \"running\" status, notifies waiters\n3. **Agentd (idle-cleanup)** -- Controller that deletes idle sandboxes after 15m inactivity\n4. **Garbage Collector** -- Background loop that cleans expired/inactive sessions from store + K8s\n5. **Store** -- Tracks `ExpiresAt` and `LastActivity` for GC queries\n\n---\n\n## 6. Proposal Format Examples\n\nThe existing AR-006 proposal at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/proposal.md` is a skeleton:\n\n```markdown\n# Proposal: AR-006 -- Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\n\n## Module\n`pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n## Language\nGo\n\n## Size\nM\n\n## Summary\n<!-- Brief description of the proposed change -->\n\n## Motivation\n<!-- Why should we do this? -->\n\n## Proposed Changes\n<!-- High-level description of what will change -->\n\n## Impact\n<!-- What systems/components are affected? -->\n```\n\nThe **best reference for format** is **AR-005** (`changes/AR-005/proposal.md`) which is the most complete and relevant proposal. Its structure:\n\n```markdown\n# AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\n\n## 概述\n[1-2 paragraph summary]\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n\n## 目的\n[Detailed purpose with numbered goals]\n\n## 范围\n### 包含\n[Numbered list of what's in scope]\n### 不包含\n[Numbered list of what's out of scope]\n\n## 影响分析\n### 直接影响\n[Table: Component | Impact | Description]\n### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n[Table: Component | Dependency]\n### 无影响的组件\n[Bullet list]\n\n## 备选方案\n### 方案 A：...（已选）\n**优点**：... **缺点**：...\n### 方案 B：...\n**优点**：... **缺点**：... **否决**（reason）\n\n## 验收标准\n[Numbered acceptance criteria]\n\n## 状态\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证\n```\n\nThe companion files are:\n- `changes/AR-006/design.md` -- Technical design with sections: Overview, Context, Goals, Non-Goals, Design, Alternatives Considered\n- `changes/AR-006/tasks.md` -- Implementation/Testing/Documentation task checklists\n\n---\n\n## 7. Relevant Constants, Configs, and Enums for Sandbox States\n\n### Sandbox Status Values (string-based, no formal enum):\n| Value | Meaning |\n|-------|---------|\n| `\"pending\"` | Sandbox CR created, waiting for running |\n| `\"running\"` | Pod is running, IP resolved, ready for use |\n\n### Timeouts and Defaults:\n| Constant | Value | Used By |\n|----------|-------|---------|\n| `DefaultSandboxTTL` | 8 hours | Sandbox `lifecycle.shutdownTime` |\n| `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` | 15 minutes | Sandbox annotation `idle-timeout` |\n| `SessionExpirationTimeout` | 15 minutes (agentd) | Idle cleanup deletion threshold |\n| GC interval | 15 seconds | Garbage collector tick |\n| Creation wait timeout | 2 minutes | `WatchSandboxOnce` select |\n| Rollback timeout | 30 seconds | `rollbackCR` context |\n| GC tick timeout | 2 minutes | Per-tick context |\n| HTTP shutdown timeout | 15 seconds | Server graceful shutdown |\n| Token cache TTL | 5 minutes | LRU cache entries |\n| Token cache capacity | 1000 | LRU cache max entries |\n\n### Sandbox CR Lifecycle Spec (from creation code):\n```go\nspec := map[string]interface{}{\n    \"replicas\": int64(1),\n    \"lifecycle\": map[string]interface{}{\n        \"shutdownTime\": shutdownTime.Format(time.RFC3339),\n    },\n}\n```\n\n### Key file paths for your reference:\n- **WorkloadManager source**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/`\n- **AR-006 proposal**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/proposal.md`\n- **AR-006 design**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md`\n- **AR-006 tasks**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md`\n- **Best proposal reference (AR-005)**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md`\n- **Sandbox orchestration spec**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`\n- **Sandbox orchestration design**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md`\n- **Idle cleanup spec**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n- **Session store design**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md`\n- **Project context**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28